Classes in org.epochx.op used by org.epochx.core
Crossover
          Crossover operators perform the task of exchanging genetic material between two programs.
Initialiser
          Initialiser implementations perform the task of generating an initial set of programs.
Mutation
          Mutation operators perform the task of manipulating a single program.
PoolSelector
          Pool selector operators perform the task of selecting a pool of programs from a population of programs.
ProgramSelector
          Program selectors perform the task of selecting individuals from a population to be used as input to genetic operators.
